<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - 教育课件平台</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-lg">
                <div class="card-body text-center p-5">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-success" style="font-size: 5rem;"></i>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h2 class="text-success mb-3">支付成功！</h2>
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-4">
                        恭喜您成功升级为VIP会员！现在您可以访问平台上的所有课件了。
                    </p>

                    <div class="vip-welcome bg-gradient text-white p-4 rounded mb-4" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);">
                        <h4 class="mb-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-crown me-2"></i>欢迎成为VIP会员
                        </h4>
                        <p class="mb-0">您现在拥有所有VIP特权</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row text-start mb-4">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h6>您的VIP特权包括：</h6>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li class="mb-1">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>
                                    访问所有付费课件
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-1">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>
                                    无限次观看学习
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h6>额外福利：</h6>
                            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                <li class="mb-1">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>
                                    优先获得新课程
                                </li>
                                <li class="mb-1">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check text-success me-2"></i>
                                    专属客服支持
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>开始探索课件
                        </a>
                        <a href="/upload" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">
                            <i class="fas fa-upload me-2"></i>上传我的课件
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html> 